# Cloudinary Setup:
# 1. Create a free account at https://cloudinary.com
# 2. Go to Settings > Upload > Upload Presets
# 3. Create an UNSIGNED preset named "pegasus_unsigned"
# 4. Copy your Cloud Name from the Dashboard

